OL,3,CJohnny Mercer accuses Labour opponent
OL,4,Cof lying about military service
OL,6,FThe Veterans' Minister Johnny Mercer
OL,7,Fhas accused his Labour opponent of
OL,8,Flying about his military service.
OL,10,FMr Mercer, an ex-Army captain turned
OL,11,Fgovernment minister, is the
OL,12,FConservative candidate for Plymouth
OL,13,FMoor View.
OL,15,FDuring a hustings event in the city,
OL,16,FMr Mercer was filmed accusing Fred
OL,17,FThomas - the Labour Party's
OL,18,Fparliamentary candidate for the
OL,19,Fconstituency - of lying about the
OL,20,Fnature of his service.
