OL,3,CJohnny Mercer accuses Labour opponent
OL,4,Cof lying about military service
OL,6,FMr Thomas is a former Royal Marine and
OL,7,Fsays he is "proud" to have served his
OL,8,Fcountry for seven years, rising to the
OL,9,Frank of Captain.
OL,11,FThe Labour Party told ITV News he
OL,12,Fremains "unable to discuss" much of
OL,13,Fhis service due to the "highly
OL,14,Fsensitive and recent nature" of his
OL,15,Frole.
OL,17,FIn a clip from the hustings, shared by
OL,18,Fthe Labour Party, Mr Mercer says:
OL,19,F"This man has claimed he has led
OL,20,Ftroops in combat. He never has.
