OL,3,CJohnny Mercer accuses Labour opponent
OL,4,Cof lying about military service
OL,6,FMr Healey said: "The Commanding
OL,7,FOfficer of the Special Forces Support
OL,8,FGroup wrote of Fred's integrity and
OL,9,Fhis character. Those words will not
OL,10,Fhave been penned lightly."
OL,12,FIn a statement, Fred Thomas said: "I
OL,13,Fam proud of having served my country
OL,14,Ffor seven years, including overseas on
OL,15,Foperations.
OL,17,F"I remain unable to discuss much of my
OL,18,Fservice, something which Johnny Mercer
OL,19,F` as a former Defence Minister ` is
OL,20,Fkeenly aware of."
