OL,3,CJohnny Mercer accuses Labour opponent
OL,4,Cof lying about military service
OL,6,FIn a post on X, formerly known as
OL,7,FTwitter, Mr Mercer described the
OL,8,Fhustings as "one of the most
OL,9,Funpleasant experiences I've had in
OL,10,Fpublic life".
OL,12,FFollowing the event, he said in a
OL,13,Fstatement: "I have always deeply
OL,14,Frespected everybody's service,
OL,15,Firrespective of what they did and
OL,16,Fwhen."
