OL,3,CJohnny Mercer accuses Labour opponent
OL,4,Cof lying about military service
OL,6,FHe said that serving "in combat" has
OL,7,F"a special meaning and carries
OL,8,F"special responsibilities", adding:
OL,9,F"That you would lie about this I find
OL,10,Futterly bewildering.
OL,12,F"I don't dispute that Fred Thomas
OL,13,Fserved in the Royal Marines or indeed
OL,14,Fconducted one operational tour where
OL,15,Fhe found himself in "challenging
OL,16,Fenvironments"; on the contrary, I
OL,17,Frespect his service.
