OL,3,CJohnny Mercer accuses Labour opponent
OL,4,Cof lying about military service
OL,6,F"But I will never allow those who seek
OL,7,Fto bloat their military records off
OL,8,Fthe back of us who did actually fight,
OL,9,Fto disrespect that sacrifice and
OL,10,Fbravery in this way - I don't care who
OL,11,Fyou are. He should resign immediately."
OL,13,FThe Plymouth Moor View constituency is
OL,14,Fa Labour target for the general
OL,15,Felection, with Mr Mercer trying to
OL,16,Fdefend a 2019 majority of 12,897.
OL,18,FSarah Martin is standing for the
OL,19,FLiberal Democrats, Shaun Hooper for
OL,20,FReform UK, and Georgia Nelson for the
OL,21,FGreen Party.
